highlights.text: “Guess featuring Billie Eilish” by Charli xcx and Billie Eilish is the highest new entry on Top Songs Israel at #38.
“אם את חייבת/אינטרו” by Vibe Ish is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Israel, up 90 spots at #72.
Omer Adam has the most spots on Top Songs Israel. “ראיתי עולם” is the highest at #8.
“לשוב הביתה” by Ishay Ribo has been on Top Songs Israel the longest, at 335 weeks straight.
